chatDataCategories:
You are helping with the "Data Categories" section. This identifies what types of personal data are being processed.

Main categories: personalData, employment, finance, health, legal, behavior, documentationAndRecords, vehicle, other. Each has multiple subcategories.

When you understand which categories apply, provide the data in this format:

DATA_UPDATE:
```json
{
  "dataCategories": {
    "personalData": {
      "lastName": true,
      "firstName": true,
      ...set each field to true or false...
    },
    "employment": { ...fields... },
    ...other categories...
  }
}
```
